為水警提供協助；駐港英軍亦經常聯同香港警方進行海陸空搜救任務<ref name="hq-1988-04-17">{{cite journal |title=巡邏艦已尋獲機器故障遊艇 |journal=華僑日報 |date=1988-04-17 |page=p.6 |url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/search-result?p_p_id=search_WAR_mmisportalportlet&p_p_lifecycle=0&p_p_state=normal&_search_WAR_mmisportalportlet_keywords=%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F%E8%89%A6&_search_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F%E8%89%A6&p_r_p_-1078056564_show_for_all_ages=&p_r_p_-1078056564_sort_field=score&_search_WAR_mmisportalportlet_mode=Basic&p_r_p_-1078056564_new_search=true&p_r_p_-1078056564_q=%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F%E8%89%A6&p_r_p_-1078056564_sort_order=desc&p_r_p_-1078056564_collection_type=Newspaper&p_r_p_-1078056564_freetext_filter=&p_r_p_-1078056564_curr_page=1&p_r_p_-1078056564_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F%E8%89%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F%E8%89%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F%E8%89%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F%E8%89%A6%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F%E8%89%A6%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F%E8%89%A6%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20dc.category.category%3A%28Newspaper%29%20%29%20%29&p_r_p_-1078056564_filter=&_search_WAR_mmisportalportlet_jspPage=%2Fjsp%2Fsearch%2Fcnsc05.jsp }}</ref><ref name="hq-1991-08-16"/>。

== 指揮架構 ==
[[香港總督|香港總督]]是[[英國君主|英國君主]]在香港的代表，擁有香港三軍總司令及海軍中將（Commander-in-Chief And Vice-Admiral of Hong Kong）頭銜，實權則由英國駐軍司令（Commander British Forces / CBF）行使；駐港英軍司令歷來都由英國陸軍少將或中將擔任，直至1993年2月18日為止，亦擔任[[香港特別行政區行政會議#歷史背景|行政局]]官守成員；有需要時會出席行政局會議。

